---
import DraftLayout from '../../layouts/DraftLayout.astro';
---
<DraftLayout title="Subtle Somatics — Gentle Transformation Within & Beyond" activeNav="home">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Subtle Somatics</p>
      <h1>Come home to the wisdom of your body</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics for those ready to meet themselves at the depth where transformation naturally unfolds.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-filled">Book a Free Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="#philosophy" class="btn">Explore</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">About Kaja</p>
        <h2>Unfolding companion. Wholeness witnesser. Integration facilitator.</h2>
        <p>I work with the natural intelligence of your body-mind-soul system — where sensations begin to speak, energy reorganises from the depth, and something deeply resonant in you starts moving through silent presence.</p>
        <p>This work is not about fixing or striving. It's about entering the field where what's true begins to reveal itself, in its own rhythm and time.</p>
        <a href="/draft/about" class="link-arrow">More about my journey &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy / Signal Pool -->
  <section class="philosophy" id="philosophy">
    <div class="philosophy-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center">What if everything we need is already here?</h2>
      <p class="text-center philosophy-sub">Subtle Somatics is not technique — it is cartography for the landscapes beneath language. Here, the body is not analyzed, but deeply and attentively listened to — each sensation a doorway, each holding a request for recognition.</p>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">01</span>
          <h3>An encounter</h3>
          <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">02</span>
          <h3>An unfolding</h3>
          <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — in the form of strength, love, presence and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar-num">03</span>
          <h3>An integration</h3>
          <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section" id="services">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center">Two pathways, one intention</p>
    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem">Services</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <a href="/draft/coaching" class="service-card">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p>Meet yourself where you are in life — at the depth where you are vastly resourced to be with life's complexity. Through deepening self-contact, you begin to encounter the vast resources beneath habitual patterns.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Explore Coaching &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/draft/spinal-energetics" class="service-card">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p>A subtle-and-powerful modality combining sound, touch, movement and music to relax the nervous system and connect you deeper with your innate qualities of strength, love, radiance and trust.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Explore Spinal Energetics &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to expect -->
  <section class="expect">
    <div class="expect-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center">What to expect</h2>
      <p class="text-center expect-sub">Each step unfolds at its own pace — no rushing, no forcing.</p>
      <div class="expect-grid">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">01</span>
          <h4>Discovery Call</h4>
          <p>A free conversation to sense into whether this work resonates. I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll feel into the right next step.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">~20 min · Free</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">02</span>
          <h4>Your Session</h4>
          <p>Each session meets you exactly where you are. Whether coaching, spinal energetics, or both — the body leads, and I follow.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">~60 min · €130</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">03</span>
          <h4>Integration</h4>
          <p>Deeper transformation unfolds over time. A series of sessions supports sustained embodiment of your wholeness.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">Series of 5 · at your own pace</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Poetic break -->
  <section class="poetic-break">
    <blockquote>
      <p>To practice subtle somatics is to return to the body not as vessel, but as a field — alive, aware, and already knowing.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- Image break -->
  <section class="image-break">
    <img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="Kaja ��� presence and embodiment" />
    <div class="ib-overlay"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Get in Touch</p>
        <h2>Ready to begin?</h2>
        <p>I'd love to have you and feel honoured to serve you — just where you are.</p>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Email</h4>
            <a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Sessions</h4>
            <p>Online (Zoom) &amp; in person</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Location</h4>
            <p>Vienna, Austria</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form class="contact-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/connect@subtlesomatics.space" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from subtlesomatics.space (draft)" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://subtlesomatics.space/draft" />
        <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" />
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message <span class="required">*</span></label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="What's alive for you right now?" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-filled">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</DraftLayout>

<style>
  .hero { position: relative; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; }
  .hero-bg img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13,13,15,0.7) 0%, rgba(13,13,15,0.4) 40%, rgba(13,13,15,0.75) 100%); }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; padding: 2rem; margin-left: 8%; margin-top: 4rem; }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 550px; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }

  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-image img { border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.3; }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .link-arrow { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .link-arrow:hover { color: var(--accent-light); }

  .philosophy { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 6rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .philosophy-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .philosophy h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; }
  .philosophy-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 4rem; }
  .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; }
  .pillar { padding: 2rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .pillar-num { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--accent-glow); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .pillar h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pillar p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .service-card { display: block; background: var(--bg-surface); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s; text-decoration: none; }
  .service-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .service-img img { width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; filter: brightness(0.85); transition: filter 0.3s; }
  .service-card:hover .service-img img { filter: brightness(1); }
  .service-body { padding: 2rem; }
  .service-body h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .service-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .service-body .link-arrow { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

  .expect { background: var(--bg-warm); padding: 6rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .expect-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .expect h2 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .expect-sub { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 auto 3rem; font-style: italic; }
  .expect-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; }
  .expect-item { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .expect-num { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .expect-item h4 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .expect-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .expect-detail { font-size: 0.8rem !important; color: var(--accent) !important; margin-top: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .poetic-break { padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: var(--bg-deep); }
  .poetic-break blockquote { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .poetic-break p { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; max-width: none; }

  .image-break { position: relative; height: 50vh; overflow: hidden; }
  .image-break img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; filter: brightness(0.7); }
  .ib-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(13,13,15,0.1), rgba(13,13,15,0.4)); }

  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .contact-text > p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .contact-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .contact-item h4 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .contact-item p, .contact-item a { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .form-group label { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .required { color: var(--accent); }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-surface);
    color: var(--text-primary); transition: border-color 0.3s; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content { margin-left: 0; }
    .about-grid, .services-grid, .pillars, .expect-grid, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .image-break { height: 35vh; }
  }
</style>
